        {
            "title": "中國已收到加入川普加沙和平委員會的邀請 暫未表明是否會接受",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"Photographer: Andrew Harnik/Getty Images AsiaPac\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/WWFMvb3Pv9ENj3MyIYZKkQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/be85e735c5a12761d5f36c831b0f18d8\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">Photographer: Andrew Harnik/Getty Images AsiaPac</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 在美國總統唐納德·川普即將在達沃斯推進加沙計畫之際，中國已收到加入其加沙和平委員會的邀請。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">中國外交部發言人郭嘉昆周二在北京舉行的例行記者會上表示：「中方已收到美方的邀請。」他未進一步說明北京是否會接受邀請。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"去年10月在韓國，美國總統唐納德·川普與中國國家主席習近平攝影師：Andrew Harnik/Getty Images AsiaPac\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/FokDIe5GmD7k_vaBmma.rA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/b2eaffec53601db6931f0d25cb00328b\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">去年10月在韓國，美國總統唐納德·川普與中國國家主席習近平攝影師：Andrew Harnik/Getty Images AsiaPac</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">川普已邀請多位世界領導人成為該委員會的創始成員，其中包括俄羅斯總統弗拉基米爾·普丁和土耳其總統雷傑普·塔伊普·埃爾多安。此舉是他「20點計畫」的一部分，旨在確保加沙實現持久和平並推進重建。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-e29db46e-5ee6-3e0c-ad3f-3e13b4948b32-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該計畫已遭到以色列總理本雅明·內塔尼亞胡的批評。他表示，相關細節並未與以色列方面進行協調。中國過去曾推動巴勒斯坦內部對立派別和解，試圖將自身塑造為全球衝突調停者的角色。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">川普還暗示，將對拒絕邀請者進行報復。在得知法國總統埃馬紐埃爾·馬克龍將拒絕加入後，川普威脅要對香檳徵收高額關稅作為回應。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題China Receives US Invitation to Join Trump’s Gaza Board of Peace</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%B7%B2%E6%94%B6%E5%88%B0%E5%8A%A0%E5%85%A5%E5%B7%9D%E6%99%AE%E5%8A%A0%E6%B2%99%E5%92%8C%E5%B9%B3%E5%A7%94%E5%93%A1%E6%9C%83%E7%9A%84%E9%82%80%E8%AB%8B-%E6%9A%AB%E6%9C%AA%E8%A1%A8%E6%98%8E%E6%98%AF%E5%90%A6%E6%9C%83%E6%8E%A5%E5%8F%97-093655122.html",
