        {
            "title": "特朗普說對香檳徵200%關稅 回應馬克龍可能拒絕加入和平理事會",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"特朗普說對香檳徵200%關稅 回應馬克龍可能拒絕加入和平理事會\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/bpIuysEqaM.9GbFIyG7OKQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MA--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2026-01/33c624d0-f5d8-11f0-bf92-25385da77c71\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">特朗普說對香檳徵200%關稅 回應馬克龍可能拒絕加入和平理事會</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
