        {
            "title": "川普加大施壓之際 丹麥計畫在格陵蘭島全年舉行軍事演習",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 據<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:格陵蘭;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/格陵蘭\">格陵蘭</a>當地報紙報導，隨著美國加大對控制這座北極島嶼的壓力，丹麥聯合北極司令部擴大在格陵蘭的軍事演習規模，可能實現全年演習。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該司令部駐格陵蘭負責人Soren Andersen向當地報紙Sermitsiaq透露，「北極耐力」行動將比以往演習持續更久，很有可能全年開展。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Andersen表示，「格陵蘭及北約北翼防線必須得到捍衛」，訓練至關重要，「這既涉及不熟悉當地環境的丹麥部隊，也包括同樣不熟悉在這一地區開展行動的盟友部隊。」</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-00dc16df-7fe8-38d3-87d4-0e8aa162dbb2-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">丹麥媒體報導稱，周一丹麥軍隊最高軍事指揮官Peter Boysen率領一批士兵抵達格陵蘭島。這是自上周開始部署的第二批部隊。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據Sermitsiaq稱，北約去年7月、8月及9月曾在格陵蘭島舉行過軍事演習。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">隨著美國總統川普再度施壓要求控制格陵蘭島，丹麥及其他幾個北大西洋公約組織國家正加強該島的防務，此次擴大的軍事訓練正是在此背景下展開。周末川普威脅將從2月1日起對八個向該北極島嶼部署軍隊的北約盟國加徵關稅後，外交僵局仍在持續。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">丹麥外交大臣Lars Lokke Rasmussen對媒體表示，「所有支持國際法律秩序的國家都必須發聲，向川普表明這條路不可繼續走下去。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「距離2月1日還有很長時間。」他補充道。「關稅是否實施，取決於我們能否共同證明：威脅手段無法達成目標。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Denmark Plans Year-Round Greenland Drills as Trump Seeks Island</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Sanne Wass、Christian Wienberg.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%B7%9D%E6%99%AE%E5%8A%A0%E5%A4%A7%E6%96%BD%E5%A3%93%E4%B9%8B%E9%9A%9B-%E4%B8%B9%E9%BA%A5%E8%A8%88%E7%95%AB%E5%9C%A8%E6%A0%BC%E9%99%B5%E8%98%AD%E5%B3%B6%E5%85%A8%E5%B9%B4%E8%88%89%E8%A1%8C%E8%BB%8D%E4%BA%8B%E6%BC%94%E7%BF%92-102145377.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-20 19:06:03",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "川普稱在格陵蘭問題上歐盟不會強力反對",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 美國總統唐納德·川普重申美國必須得到格陵蘭，聲稱歐盟不會有太大阻力。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">周一深夜他在佛羅里達州發表講話時稱，為了對抗俄羅斯和中國的影響力，格陵蘭島是國家安全所必需的，並聲稱丹麥缺乏防禦能力。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「我們必須得到它。他們必須完成這件事。」川普在談到格陵蘭時對記者說道。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在前往達沃斯之前，川普聲稱美國經濟是全球「最火熱」的經濟。他與內政部長道格·伯格姆一同出席了論壇，並列舉了創紀錄的投資和股市高企。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-7ddf28b4-b60c-3193-ac6e-ff7159ef4f85-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Trump Repeats Greenland Claims, Says EU Won’t Push Back Hard</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%B7%9D%E6%99%AE%E7%A8%B1%E5%9C%A8%E6%A0%BC%E9%99%B5%E8%98%AD%E5%95%8F%E9%A1%8C%E4%B8%8A%E6%AD%90%E7%9B%9F%E4%B8%8D%E6%9C%83%E5%BC%B7%E5%8A%9B%E5%8F%8D%E5%B0%8D-050545180.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-20 13:40:08",
